# .gitattributes - Force LF line endings for shell scripts.
#
# This file is part of jacques-clouseau, various keen and handy inspectors.
#
# Written in 2019 by Eliah Kagan <degeneracypressure@gmail.com>.
#
# To the extent possible under law, the author(s) have dedicated all copyright
# and related and neighboring rights to this software to the public domain
# worldwide. This software is distributed without any warranty.
#
# You should have received a copy of the CC0 Public Domain Dedication along
# with this software. If not, see
# <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.

# Most files are shell scripts and should always have LF line endings.
* text eol=lf

# Files with dots in their names are text files but aren't shell scripts.
*.* text eol=auto

# Other files that are text files but not shell scripts.
/COPYING text eol=auto
